(83, 1, 1, -919, -918, 'Nadab&rsquo;s accession year as King in Israel in the 2<sup>nd</sup> year (non-accession counting) of Asa&rsquo;s reign (1 Kings 14:20; 15:25). He reigns for 2 years.', 4, 'Nadab''s !!! year as King in Israel', null, null, null, 10, '2020-12-06 22:15:57', null),
