(85, 1, 0, -905, -905, 'Judah makes a covenent to seek God in the 15<sup>th</sup> year of Asa&rsquo;s reign (2 Chronicles 15:10).', 1, null, null, null, null, 10, '2020-12-04 20:53:44', '<p>Many Israelites were deserting and going to Judah at this time (2 Chronicles 15). In that same year Baasha , King of Israel, fortified the city of Ramah (2 Chronicles 16:1). Although 2 Chronicles 16:1 states &ldquo;in the 36<sup>th</sup> year of the reign of Asa&rdquo;...it is referring to the 15th year of Asa&rsquo;s rule as King in Judea which was the 36<sup>th</sup> year of the independant Judean Kingdom.</p>'),
