(256, 1, 0, -777, -777, 'Azariah&rsquo;s (Uzziah) sole reign as King of Judah in the 27<sup>th</sup> year of Jeroboam&rsquo;s reign. He reigns for a total of 52 years. (2 Kings 15:1-2; 2 Chronicles 26:1, 3).', 7, null, null, null, null, 1, '2021-02-02 12:20:03', '<p>Azariah in 2 Kings is also known as Uzziah in 2 Chronicles. His mother, called Jecoliah in 2 Kings, is called Jechiliah in 2 Chronicles.</p>'),
(257, 1, 1, -800, -749, 'Azariah begins his co-reign with Amaziah as Kings of Judah. Azariah reigns for a total of 52 years (2 Kings 15:1-2; 2 Chronicles 26:1, 3).', 7, 'Azariah''s !!! year as King of Judah.', null, null, null, 1, '2021-02-02 12:16:09', '<p>Azariah in 2 Kings is also known as Uzziah in 2 Chronicles. His mother: Jecoliah in 2 Kings, also called Jechiliah in 2 Chronicles.</p>'),
