(261, 1, 1, -759, -731, 'Pekah is in Gilead in co-reign with Menahem. This co-reign lasts 8 years until Pekahiah&rsquo;s accession year as King in Israel begins. Pekah then co-reigns with Pekahiah for an additional 2 years during which he kills Pekahiah and begins his sole reign. He reigns solely 20 years for a total of 29 years (2 Kings 15:27, 30).', 4, 'Pekah''s !!! year as King in Israel.', null, null, null, 10, '2020-12-17 20:40:29', null),
