(285, 1, 0, -246, -221, 'Ptolemy II dies, Ptolemy III Euergetes comes to the Greek throne in Egypt (246 &ndash; 221 BC) ruling over the Ptolemic Greeks. He attacks the Seleucid Kingdom and battles them till his death in 221 BC. See commentary on Daniel 11:7.', 6, 'Ptolemy III''s !!! year as ruler of the Ptolemic Greeks from Egypt.', null, null, null, 10, '2020-12-17 21:45:33', null),
